Interface KeyspaceChangeListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Container, LockingContainer, NonLockingAltContainer, NonLockingContainer

    public interface KeyspaceChangeListener
    Since the responsibility for the portion of the keyspace that this node is responsible for is determined by the Inbound strategy, when that responsibility changes, Dempsy itself needs to be notified.
